      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so if i add the shrinkage value to the COGS, the ratio goes down, right? i just want to make sure i have the direction of the movement right for the slide deck. also, does the average inventory part stay the same, or should i be adjusting that too since the physical stock is lower now?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
